parameters:
\nc<>Quietly. They have pretty sharp senses, so if we make a
fuss, they'll catch on immediately.
\nc<>Hmm... It's much worse than I imagined.

\nc<>Most of the missing people have gathered here... and
everyone is being violated by tentacles in the same way.
\nc<>Do they not reproduce on their own, or are they unable to?

\nc<>(And all of those tentacles are connected to a massive one
in the center.

\nc<>From what I can see, that is the core or mother body where
new tentacles are born.

\nc<>What should we do, Levantia? Are you planning to jump in
right away?

\nc<>...No. There's a strange gas filling this place. Every time
I breathe, my body tingles.

\nc<>I'm sorry to everyone, but if I'm being used as a breeding
ground, I shouldn't be killed right away.
\nc<>Let's come back after making thorough preparations.
\nc<>No matter what happens this time, failure is not allowed.

\nc<>With the help of Candy and Sherbet, we can prevent this
troublesome air and make the invasoids retreat.
\nc<>So everyone, please endure just a little longer.
\nc<>I will come to help right away.
\nc<>I obtained the memory T3: Mother of the Invasoids.

\nc<>Good listeners increased by 7,000, and bad listeners
increased by 3,000.
